extracted_rules.class_0:
R1: In the first third of the series, values start moderately high and then clearly decrease toward a small minimum.  
R2: In the middle third, values rise sharply from near-minimum up to a high peak.  
R3: In the last third, values stay mostly high with only a gentle decline toward the end.
extracted_rules.class_1:
R1: In the first third of the series, values start very low and stay close to the minimum before slowly rising.  
R2: In the middle third, values rise sharply from very low to a high peak.  
R3: In the last third, values decrease steadily and strongly from the peak down to low values.

extracted_rules.class_0:
R1: Early part (time 0–5) starts higher (around 0.2–0.3) and decreases toward near 0.  
R2: Middle part (time 10–15) has a single dominant peak that is relatively high (around 0.6–0.9).  
R3: Late part (time 18–23) gradually decreases but remains at a moderate level (around 0.3–0.6), not dropping sharply to near 0.
extracted_rules.class_1:
R1: Very early part (time 0–5) starts low (near 0) and stays low or slightly decreasing.  
R2: Middle part (time 8–15) rises sharply from low to a high peak (around 0.6–0.8).  
R3: Late part (time 18–23) shows a strong, almost linear drop from moderate/high values down to near 0.

extracted_rules.class_0:
R1: The series starts at a relatively high value and then decreases quickly to a low plateau within the first 5–7 time steps.  
R2: From this low plateau, it rises steeply to a peak around time 12–14, then stays high (forming a broad, flat or slightly wavy top) until about time 18–20.  
R3: After time 18–20, it decreases gradually, remaining at a moderate level (not falling close to the starting minimum) by the end.
extracted_rules.class_1:
R1: The series starts at a low value and stays low or gently decreasing for roughly the first 6–8 time steps.  
R2: From this low region, it rises steeply to a peak around time 12–16, forming a relatively narrow top (the peak is not followed by a long, flat high plateau).  
R3: After the peak, it falls sharply and monotonically so that by the last few time steps it is close to the minimum level of the series.
